@startuml
title Outbox Event Lifecycle

[*] --> NEW : business tx committed

NEW --> PROCESSING : claimed for publish
FAILED --> PROCESSING : retry claimed
PROCESSING --> PROCESSING : stale claim reclaimed
PROCESSING --> PUBLISHED : publish success
PROCESSING --> FAILED : publish failure and retryCount < maxRetries
PROCESSING --> FATAL : publish failure and retryCount >= maxRetries

note right of PROCESSING
  claimed_at stores the claim lease timestamp.
  Stale PROCESSING rows can be claimed again.
end note

PUBLISHED --> [*]
FATAL --> [*]

@enduml
